messages.messageBody:
I have my own business. It's a catalog shopping company that I've been
with for almost 5 years. I don't stock, inventory or deliver any
products. I just set up the accounts and get paid. There's a 96%
re-order rate, the products make sense and are need based and unique to
this company which has been around for over 15 years. It gives me the
flexibility and income out family needs and I can continue to build it
and give myself my own raise. If this is the kind of business you're
looking for, feel free to e-mail me. Good Luck on your search!

Sherry
